00:21:26.630 --> 00:21:28.490
How much RAM does it have?

00:21:28.530 --> 00:21:30.070
How big of a drive does it have?

00:21:30.070 --> 00:21:32.890
Of that size of a drive,
how much space is on that drive?

00:21:32.890 --> 00:21:34.490
What operating system do I have?

00:21:34.490 --> 00:21:37.440
Which build of that operating
system is on that given machine?

00:21:37.440 --> 00:21:38.530
Is that machine here?

00:21:38.530 --> 00:21:40.190
