00:23:59.090 --> 00:24:03.300
we know that even though we have
300 machines on our network,

00:24:03.300 --> 00:24:06.620
or 3,000 machines on our network,
there's actually a lot of power

00:24:06.620 --> 00:24:07.060
points that we can use to do this.

00:24:07.060 --> 00:24:07.060
So then you can now pull this nice
little cute report and hand it back

00:24:07.060 --> 00:24:07.060
off to your pointy-haired boss,
