and says, oh, okay, here's what I need,

00:36:22.930 --> 00:36:25.600
or oh, this package is updated,
and will pull it.

00:36:25.680 --> 00:36:29.720
So if a laptop is home for three months,
it comes back on the network,

00:36:29.810 --> 00:36:32.990
or they VPN in into our network,
